HEADWORD: Bragget
<hw>Brag"get</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>braket</ets>, <ets>bragot</ets>, fr. W. <ets>bragawd</ets>,
<ets>bragod</ets>, fr. <ets>brag</ets> malt.]</ety> <def>A liquor made
of ale and honey fermented, with spices, etc.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
